{"tid":1677534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報文匯報究竟幾時死","createTime":"2019-10-27T07:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T07:20:18.000Z","uid":271742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eb384236904fc1fd0c1209a2f9b8f21da9b93997","tid":1677534,"uid":271742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"唔知各位巴絲有幾多人屋企係深藍<br />\n我屋企就藍到發紅嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆就係嗰啲貪心到仆街嘅人<br />\n啫係偷廁紙偷牙膏搶紙皮個啲<br />\n然後佢最撚鍾意嘅就係<span style=\"color: red;\">免費報紙</span><br />\n運動開始以嚟每日檯頭就會有份大共文匯<br />\n成份野莫講話參與過運動唔會信<br />\n稍為有睇過其他新聞或者夜晚望下窗口都知咩事<br />\n但係依啲睇到眼火爆fake news<span style=\"color: red;\">其實係好撚勁嘅文宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n耳濡目染<br />\n每日兩份夾埋<span style=\"color: red;\">二三百</span>個「暴徒」「曱甴」真係洗晒佢哋啲廢腦<br />\n依家屋企好耐無開cctvb<br />\n因為兩條廢老覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">cctvb好撚黃</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣入到屋企同入唔到屋企個效果差好撚遠</span><br />\n當然過咗咁耐要歸邊嘅都歸咗<br />\n但係請大家唔好<span style=\"color: red;\">忽視fake news嘅威力</span><br />\n無論係對家又好自己嘅都好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">耳濡目染嘅fake news係可以完全摧毀同重建一個人嘅價值觀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntldr：假新聞可唔可以快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44396a5368c114d0bbb2b72fbecd5700934fd0e","tid":1677534,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb550dd145f894f478a141897e4d2819abaf2ec","tid":1677534,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T07:20:18.000Z","msg":"沒有消費就沒有關注 沒有關注就等於消失<br />\n成日推佢消息就緊係唔會死啦"}]}